data_table.description: Brain MRI Measurements Method 1, Original, Offspring, Generation 3, New Offspring Spouse, Omni 1, and Omni 2. Brain MRI was performed between 3/1999 to 8/2011. Two methods have been used to read brain MRIs at Framingham to date to define lobes. Method 1 is an older method and is no longer being used. Method 2 is a new method. Method 2 did not start until 2009. There are some MRI scans that have been read using both methods. Note that when this is true, the measurements may differ. This dataset contains scans read using Method 1.
